IBAN,com,operates,as,a,web,based,solution,that,supports,the,validation,and,calculation,of,International,Bank,Account,Numbers,IBAN,The,platform,provides,access,to,the,Reverse,SORT,code,that,is,a,web,based,real,time,interface,for,identifying,and,validating,SORT,codes,The,IBAN,Sort,Code,Validation,API,simplifies,the,deployment,of,the,SORT,code,verification,functionality,through,add,on,modules,Simple,calls,are,sufficient,for,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,SORT,code,functionality,in,the,applications,This,API,returns,responses,in,JSON,and,XML,formats